modName: Additional Twitch Commands for Age of Oblivion
modShortDescription: Adds commands for Age of Oblivion mod. Localized in English and Japanese.
modDescription:
Adding the following commands for [Age of Oblivion](https://7daystodiemods.com/age-of-oblivion/) mod. Localized in English and Japanese.

```
#spawn_animalGuard:Spawn Oblivion AnimalGuard
#spawn_humanGuard:Spawn Oblivion HumanGuard
#spawn_juggernaut:Spawn Oblivion Juggernaut
#spawn_nightWatcher1:Spawn Night Watcher A
#spawn_nightWatcher2:Spawn Night Watcher B
#spawn_nightWatcher3:Spawn Night Watcher C
#spawn_nightWatcher4:Spawn Night Watcher D
#spawn_totem1:Spawn Oblivion Tier1 Totem
#spawn_totem2:Spawn Oblivion Tier2 Totem
#spawn_totem3:Spawn Oblivion Tier3 Totem
#spawn_wendigo:Spawn Oblivion Wendigo
#spawn_westland:Spawn Oblivion Westland Entity
#spawn_zombieGuard:Spawn Oblivion ZombieGuard
#spawn_zombieGuardF:Spawn Oblivion ZombieGuard Feral
#spawn_zombieGuardR:Spawn Oblivion ZombieGuard Radiated
```

Also available command [copy tool](https://7daystodie.net/doku.php?id=menu_special_tools:twitch_command_tool_aoo:list) in our website.

For Twitch Streamers, we support to develop, modify your Twitch integration. Please visit our Steam group(Support link) and tell us what do you want.
